<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>&lt;0x0<sp/>0x2000<sp/>0x0<sp/>0x1000&gt;;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">};</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
